snippet.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles Arcade Direct - Cleaning Up The Sewers - (Raw Thrills)
snippet.description:
Find out more about this product at: https://primetimeamusements.com/product/teenage-mutant-ninja-turtles-2018/ - Next up in our direct capture series, it's the new Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles arcade exclusive brawler by Raw Thrills! We start off in the Sewers and subsequent videos will take you through the full game! playing as Mikey. As the beginning of the video mentions, the audio has to be captured separately from a microphone, since most arcade machines do not output audio through DVI/HDMI.

If you are in the Ft. Lauderdale area, check this game out at our Xtreme Action Park facility! https://xtremeactionpark.com/

PrimeTime Amusements is a global operator, wholesale seller and event renter of brand new and refurbished video arcade machines, simulators, redemption games and more. Based out of Ft. Lauderdale, FL, we have been in business for over 25 years.
